FATHER'S DAY GIFT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Thank you for the photographs and text by Mariana Cook ("Fathers & Daughters," 
June 19). What a great gift for Father's Day! In a world of vast deserts of 
inhumanity, they are truly an oasis of civility and culture. 
</P>
<P>
 PATRICK L. MURPHY 
</P>
<P>
 Corona 
</P>
