<TEXT>
<P>
 Tired, 
</P>
<P>
 looking for a place to stay; 
</P>
<P>
 hanging wisteria. 
</P>
<P>
 The jars of octopus --  
</P>
<P>
 brief dreams 
</P>
<P>
 under the summer moon. 
</P>
<P>
 Exciting at first, 
</P>
<P>
 then sad, 
</P>
<P>
 watching the cormorant-fishing. 
</P>
<P>
 Blowing stones 
</P>
<P>
 along the road on Mount Asama, 
</P>
<P>
 the autumn wind. 
</P>
<P>
 Seeing people off, 
</P>
<P>
 being seen off --  
</P>
<P>
 autumn in Kiso. 
</P>
<P>
 It's not like anything 
</P>
<P>
 they compare it to --  
</P>
<P>
 the summer moon. 
</P>
