<P>
BEACH BLANKET BOOKS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By E.W. Alexander, New this week: 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 DIXIE CITY JAM, by James Lee Burke. (Hyperion: $22.95). Detective Dave 
Robicheaux is beseeched by a local to investigate a sunken submarine off the 
Louisiana coast, which brings back long-forgotten memories.That WWII vessel's 
surreptitious purpose is about to be revived by a neo-Nazi. (Also available on 
