<HEADLINE>
<P>
THE MATURE TRAVELER: BOUNTEOUS DISCOUNTS AT LODGINGS IN OXNARD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By HANK KOVELL 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Less than an hour's drive north of Los Angeles, the community of Oxnard is 
attracting seniors. 
</P>
<P>
 The area is a bountiful producer of fruits and vegetables, and its annual 
Strawberry Festival attracts thousands of visitors. 
</P>
<P>
 The city's Channel Islands Harbor has nine picturesque marinas and is home to 
more than 2,500 pleasure boats and an assortment of modestly priced waterfront 
restaurants, many of which offer early-bird specials for senior patrons. 
</P>
<P>
 Participating Oxnard hotels that offer special rates or packages for seniors 
include the following: 
</P>
<P>
 * Casa Sirena Marina Resorts offers a guest room and full breakfast for two 
for $69 per night. Regular rate for room only is $85; tel. (805) 985-6311. 
</P>
<P>
 * Country Inn at Port Hueneme offers a deluxe guest room, breakfast and 
two-hour evening cocktail reception for $72 per night for two. Regular rate is 
$85. Valid year-round; tel. (805) 986-5353. 
</P>
<P>
 * Oxnard Hilton Inn offers an exclusive membership for mature travelers with 
savings of 25% to 50% off available regular room rates. Guests receive a rate 
of $69 per room, including continental breakfast. Valid year-round; tel. (805) 
485-9666. 
</P>
<P>
 * Mandalay Beach Resort provides a spacious two-room suite, hot breakfast 
buffet and dinner for two in the Capistrano Restaurant (selection includes 
nonalcoholic beverage, taxes and tip.) Price before Sept. 1 is $135 per couple 
and from Oct. 1 to June 30, 1995, the price is $124; tel. (805) 
984-2500.(Regular rates range from $159 to $219 for two depending on location 
in the hotel.) 
</P>
<P>
 * Radisson Suite Hotel at River Ridge offers a deluxe suite with full kitchen, 
cooked-to-order breakfast, snack basket and one cocktail per adult, and 
complimentary use of five night-lighted tennis courts. Package includes choice 
of two 30-minute sets of tennis instruction for two, or for golfers, green fees 
and electric cart for 18 holes of golf. Weekday package for two with golf is 
$130, weekends $150. The tennis package is $120. Advance reservations required; 
tel. (805) 988-0130. 
</P>
<P>
 For a copy of the Senior Getaway Package, which lists all participating area 
restaurants plus details on noted package discounts in Oxnard, call the Oxnard 
Tourism Bureau at (800) 994-4852. 
</P>
</TEXT>
