<HEADLINE>
<P>
NO, NO NORWAY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Regarding "Norway's Magnetic North" (June 12): I do not know why the Los 
Angeles Times touts Norway as a travel destination when, for the second year in 
a row, Norway is whaling on minke whales (smallest baleen whale), in violation 
of the 1986 moratorium on whaling and despite universal censure. Lofoten should 
not be a tourist destination until Norway ceases whaling. 
</P>
<P>
 MARIS SIDENSTECKER, Director, Save the Whales, Venice 
</P>
