<DOCNO> LA072494-0212 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 063607 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
July 24, 1994, Sunday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 2; Column 5; Metro Desk 
</P>
