<HEADLINE>
<P>
SCHEDULE OF EVENTS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The 48th annual San Fernando Valley Fair concludes today at the Los Angeles 
Equestrian Center, 480 Riverside Drive, Burbank. Hours are 10 a.m. to 10:30 
p.m. Admission is $5 per person, with children 11 and younger admitted free. 
</P>
<P>
 Parking on the fairgrounds is $3. Free satellite parking and a shuttle bus are 
also offered. Fair information: (818) 373-4500. Fair parking information: (818) 
373-4516. TIME: TODAY'S EVENTS 
