attractive to NAIA and small NCAA schools. These smaller schools had more men's 
soccer programs than football programs in 1993-94. 03,14,08,10 Soccer Football 
Division I 194 221 Division II 127 142 Division III 288 198 NAIA 253 117 A 
LEAGUE OF THEIR OWN 
</P>
